description: Rails is a full-stack, open source web framework that enables you to create full-featured, sophisticated web-based applications, but with a twist. A full Rails application probably has less total code than the XML you'd need to configure the same application in other frameworks. With this book you'll learn how to use to connect business objects and database tables.
